column2: Crusader Kings 2: Great Works — Part 1 - Also Sprach Zarathustra
column7:
With the new free Great Works expansion for Crusader Kings II, we can now control famous landmarks and build new ones of our own. In this campaign, we will be attempting to build some wonders in our realm as we restore the Persian Empire and Zoroastrianism to the Iranian Plateau, while becoming the Saoshyant and trying to gain the achievement "The One Who Brings Benefit."

---------------------------------------------

The series is best viewed from the playlist:
